【贵系注意】SAP北京实验室招实习生，每月4000元起
1319
<p>各位贵系的学弟学妹学长学姐，</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SAP北京实验室想在清华招收一些实习生，贵系同学当然是首选了，本研均可申请。我所在的软件所数据库组和SAP有着良好的合作关系，所以被录取的机会还是很大的，强烈建议大家申请。下面是具体的介绍和要求。</p><p>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;line-height: 1.5;">1、介绍</span></p><p>Introduction to TIP CE&amp;SP China</p><p>CE&amp;SP(Customer Engagement &amp; Strategic Projects) with a workforce of 450 employees(in China, USA, Germany and India) belongs to Technology &amp; Innovation Platform Board Area, that is led by Dr. Vishal Sikka - Chief Technology Officer and Member of SAP Executive Board.</p><p>CE&amp;SP China, led by Dr. Li Wen-Syan - Global Vice President, is located at SAP Labs China, Shanghai Pudong Software Park. It opened up a branch office in Raycom Building, Beijing Zhongguancun Science &amp; Technology Park.</p><p>    <img src="http://fmn.rrimg.com/fmn065/20130709/1200/large_RvA7_26770000c13b125f.jpg" border="0" thumbnail="http://fmn.rrimg.com/fmn065/20130709/1200/main_RvA7_26770000c13b125f.jpg" title="photo-media"></p><p>关于SAP和该实验室的详细介绍可以自行搜索或点击<a href="http://rrurl.cn/hmgNdB " target="_blank">这里</a>下载Introduction。</p><p>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">2、要求</span></p><p>SAP的工作氛围很好，要求每周一到周五上班，一般十点到公司即可，没有加班，工作地点离清华很近，就在保福寺桥的融科中心，骑车大概十几分钟就到了，实习时间可以是暑期也可以长期。</p><p>欢迎各位贵系的大牛小牛们申请啊！在本周日（7.14）前将简历发到我的邮箱（wanghenan09@gmail.com）即可。欢迎申请，欢迎咨询！</p>
