 Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">6</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">月</span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">24</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">日</span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">9:56</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><a href="http://news.huochepiao.com/vote.asp?Filename=201162495632.htm"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">投它一票</span></span></span></a><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">来源：</span></span><a href="http://www.qianlong.com/"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">千龙网</span></span></span></a><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">[</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://news.huochepiao.com/comment.asp?action=list&Filename=201162495632.htm">评论</a></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">] [</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">字号：<a>大</a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;</span></span><a><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">中</span></span></a><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a>小</a></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">]</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0.05cm;margin-bottom: 0.05cm;line-height: 0.74cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">    <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">为满足广大人民群众多种方式购买火车票的需求，减少旅客集中到车站、火车票代售处排队购票，北京铁路局推出火车票电话订票新业务。从</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">2011</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">年</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">6</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">月</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">25</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">日起，旅客拨打订票电话</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">95105105</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">即可预订</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">3</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">日后至电话订票系统确定的车票预售期内各次列车的车票。 </span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0.05cm;margin-bottom: 0.05cm;line-height: 0.74cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">　　据介绍，此次北京铁路局推出的电话订票系统具有电话订票和信息查询等多项功能，采用自助语音提示，无人工干扰，同一时间可以接通</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">8000</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">位旅客的订票需求，操作简便，易学易懂。旅客可根据电话语音提示，预订第</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">3</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">天（含发车日）至电话订票系统预售期（电话订票系统预售期优先于售票窗口</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">24</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">小时）内各次列车的全票、儿童票、学生票和残疾军人车票；当日和次日的车票不开通电话订票业务。预订其它票种须到车站指定窗口办理。同时，此系统还可办理电话订票单的查询、取消等业务，并提供列车的时刻、票价、余票情况以及电话区号、取票地址等相关信息的查询业务。</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0.05cm;margin-bottom: 0.05cm;line-height: 0.74cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">　　预定成功后，市民可凭电话订票系统提供的订单号、订票时使用的有效证件原件</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">(</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">建议使用二代身份证</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">)</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">在北京铁路局管内任一车站指定的窗口或火车票代售点办理取票。订购学生票，取票时需出示学生证，刷学生优惠卡进行取票。订购残疾军人票，需持有效证件到车站指定窗口办理取票。旅客需由他人代取车票时，须同时出示订票人和取票人的身份证原件，经确认后方可出票。</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0.05cm;margin-bottom: 0.05cm;line-height: 0.74cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0.05cm;margin-bottom: 0.05cm;line-height: 0.74cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0.05cm;margin-bottom: 0.05cm;line-height: 0.74cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">&nbsp;</p><p>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">二、到达厦门（<span style="font-family: Cambria , serif;">30</span>日晚到达，入住如家快捷酒店）</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">时间：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">7.30</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">到达厦门，正点到达的时间是<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">19:27</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">，很可能晚点。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">费用：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">246X0.8</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">，会员卡应该会打折吧。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">备注：由于火车可能晚点，所以到达厦门的时间可能会比较晚，可能<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">点或<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">9</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">点吧，建议就近住在</span><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><strong>如家火车站广场店</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">，离火车站只有<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">300</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">米。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">如家预订：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="LEFT">    <span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">1</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">、艺龙网：</span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="color: rgb(79,129,189);"><a href="http://hotel.elong.com/search/list_cn_1401.html?&q=%u5982%u5BB6%u5FEB%u6377%u9152%u5E97%uFF08%u53A6%u95E8%u706B%u8F66%u7AD9%u5E7F%u573A%u5E97%uFF09&qt=9">http://hotel.elong.com/search/list_cn_1401.html?&amp;q=%u5982%u5BB6%u5FEB%u6377%u9152%u5E97%uFF08%u53A6%u95E8%u706B%u8F66%u7AD9%u5E7F%u573A%u5E97%uFF09&amp;qt=9#</a>?</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">    <span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">2</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">、如家官网（</span><strong>推荐</strong><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">）：</span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><a href="http://www.homeinns.com/Resv/hotel.aspx?CityCd=0592&StartDate=2011-07-30&EndDate=2011-07-31&LandMark=0003"><span style="color: rgb(79,129,189);">http://www.homeinns.com/Resv/hotel.aspx?CityCd=0592&amp;StartDate=2011-07-30&amp;EndDate=2011-07-31&amp;LandMark=000</span></a></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">    <img src="http://fmn.rrfmn.com/fmn048/20110729/2255/b_large_C1JO_028b0007a9755c3f.jpg" border="0">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-indent: 0.74cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">图一 厦门如家火车站广场店信息</p><p style="text-indent: 0.74cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <img src="http://fmn.rrfmn.com/fmn048/20110729/2255/b_large_vLBs_582e000855535c72.jpg" border="0"></p><p style="text-indent: 0.74cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">图二 厦门火车站和如家的相对位置</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><h2>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">三、鼓浪屿之行（从如家火车站广场店出发）</span></h2><p style="margin-top: 0.21cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;line-height: 0.48cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">    <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">乘车：</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0.21cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;line-height: 0.48cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">    <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">起点：厦门如家火车站广场店 终点：鼓浪屿</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">乘</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">952/955/957/129</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">(</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">火车站上，经</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">8</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">站，轮渡下</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">)</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">，约</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">35</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">分钟。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">备注：鼓浪屿的攻略可以看这个日志：</span></span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><a href="/share/231279771/7582389059"><span style="color: rgb(79,129,189);">http://blog.renren.com/share/231279771/7582389059</span></a></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-size: x-small;">下面的日志可能更好些：</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><a href="/share/283887444/5340690898"><span style="color: rgb(79,129,189);">http://blog.renren.com/share/283887444/5340690898</span></a></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;<img src="http://fmn.rrfmn.com/fmn048/20110729/2255/b_large_sAgU_57f6000857855c72.jpg" border="0"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">图三 厦门火车站和鼓浪屿的相对位置</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">我的小建议：</p><p style="text-indent: 0.64cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">在鼓浪屿上可以玩儿两天或者三天，<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">31</span>日上午从如家酒店出发，乘公交车到鼓浪屿轮渡，坐船上岛，找到住的酒店（或者提前预定），开玩儿。</p><ol>    <li>        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">第二天（<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8.1</span>）可以继续在岛上逛，下午回到厦门，可以就近去厦大玩儿，厦大附近也有一家如家，可以住在厦大的如家，或者<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">回到市区</span>。</p>    </li>    <li>        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">第二天继续在岛上逛，并且晚上继续住在岛上，第三天（<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8.2</span>）上午回到厦门，就近去厦大玩儿，下午<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">回到市区</span>。</p>    </li></ol><p style="margin-left: 0.74cm;text-indent: -0.74cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">注：厦门火车站是在厦门比较中心的位置，到哪儿都挺方便的，所以不妨<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">回到市区</span>就住在火车站附近吧。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><h2>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">四、厦大之行（从如家火车站广场店出发）</span></h2><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">乘车：</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;line-height: 0.48cm;widows: 2;orphans: 2;" align="LEFT">    <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">起点：厦门如家火车站广场店 终点：厦门大学</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">乘</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">122/48</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">(</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">火车站上，经</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">13</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">站，厦大医院下</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">)</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">，约</span></span><span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 宋体 , serif;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">49</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(93,93,93);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">分钟。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">备注：可以看出厦大离鼓浪屿真的很近，可以去鼓浪屿玩儿完之后到厦大玩儿，可以去厦大的校区、海滩、植物园，厦大南边好像还有南普陀山，可以去拜佛。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;<img src="http://fmn.xnpic.com/fmn050/20110729/2255/b_large_PusD_580200084e815c72.jpg" border="0"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">图四 厦门火车站和厦大的相对位置</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><h2>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">五、泉州之行</span></h2><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">火车票信息：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><a href="http://lieche.huoche.com/zz-xiamen-quanzhouzhan/">http://lieche.huoche.com/zz-xiamen-quanzhouzhan/</a></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">    <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">备注：厦门离泉州很近，动车只需要半个小时，注意有的是从厦门北发车，有的是从厦门站发车，从厦门站发车的要<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">40</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">多分钟，从厦门北发车的要<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">20</span></span><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">多分钟。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;<img src="http://fmn.rrimg.com/fmn051/20110729/2255/b_large_J5l5_025a0007a96a5c3f.jpg" border="0"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">图五 厦门和泉州的相对位置</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;<img src="http://fmn.rrimg.com/fmn051/20110729/2255/b_large_N1CN_66980007aa6d5c43.jpg" border="0"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">图六 泉州到<a href="http://www.hudong.com/wiki/%E5%B4%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>崇武古镇</strong></span></a>约<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">40</span>公里，行车<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">1</span>小时<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">（泉州同学推荐）</span></p><h2>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">六、返程 飞机（<span style="font-family: Cambria , serif;">5</span>日厦门飞北京）</span></h2><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">目前的票价是这样的，貌似蛮贵的：</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;<img src="http://fmn.rrimg.com/fmn054/20110729/2255/b_large_uhD9_3b36000854e15c71.jpg" border="0"></p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">    <a name="_GoBack"></a> 图七 <span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8</span>月<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">5</span>日厦门到北京机票价格</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 1.16cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="CENTER">&nbsp;</p><h2>    <span style="font-size: 18.0pt;">七、小结</span></h2><p style="text-indent: 0.74cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">三个女生游厦门真的挺让人担心的啊，所以凡事要机灵一点。刚刚和隔壁的泉州的同学聊了一下，他说福建可以玩儿的地方也就是武夷山和厦门了，既然你们不想爬山那就只有厦门了，在厦门可以去鼓浪屿（<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">2</span>天：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">7.31,8.1</span>），厦大附近（<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">1</span>天：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8.2</span>），泉州（<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">2</span>天：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8.3</span>，<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8.4</span>）厦门本岛（<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">1</span>天：<span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;">8.5</span>）。在厦门还好，交通方便，人口稠密，比较安全，但是泉州就相对条件差一些了，所以如果没有把握的话也可以不去，替代为去杭州、广州，或者上海一类的。泉州比较好的是<a href="http://www.hudong.com/wiki/%E5%B4%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>崇武古镇</strong></span></a>，但是离泉州市区有些远，具体可以看介绍。</p><p style="text-indent: 0.74cm;margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">最后，祝你们旅途顺利！</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="RIGHT">    <span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 华文行楷 , serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>By </strong></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 华文行楷;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>王鹤男</strong></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;" align="RIGHT">    <span style="font-family: DejaVu Serif , serif;"><span style="font-family: 华文行楷 , serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>2011.7.19</strong></span></span></span></p>
