.10-dev</span>     <br>     <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">sudo apt-get install intltool</span>     <br>     <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">sudo apt-get install libsqlite3-dev</span>     <br>     <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">sudo apt-get install libnm-glib-dev</span>     <br>     <span style="color: rgb(0,0,0);font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">sudo apt-get install libxss-dev</span>     <br>     <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">4.然后在终端中依次输入：</span>     <br>     <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">cd 解压后的文件夹的位置</span>     <br>     <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">./configure</span>     <br>     <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">make</span>     <br>     <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">sudo make install</span>     <br>     <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">5.然后在终端中依次输入：<br>cd /etc<br>sudo vi ld.so.conf<br>         <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">在ld.so.conf这个文件中加入一行：include /usr/local/lib，保存退出</span>。<br>         <span style="color: rgb(255,0,0);">sudo ldconfig</span></span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 14.0pt;">如果不进行这步可能会导致程序不能启动。<br>应该就可以正常使用了了。</span></p>
